verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> ye the <S%H3050>LORD.<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> <S%H853><s%> the <S%H3068>LORD,<s%> O my <S%H5315>soul.<s%>
While I <S%H2416>live<s%> will I <S%H1984>praise<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD:<s%> I will sing <S%H2167>praises<s%> unto my <S%H430>God<s%> while I have any <S%H5750>being.<s%>
Put <S%H408>not<s%> your <S%H982>trust<s%> in <S%H5081>princes,<s%> nor in the <S%H1121>son<s%> of <S%H120>man,<s%> in whom there is <S%H7945>no<s%> <S%H369><s%> <S%H8668>help.<s%>
His <S%H7307>breath<s%> goeth <S%H3318>forth,<s%> he <S%H7725>returneth<s%> to his <S%H127>earth;<s%> in that <S%H1931>very<s%> <S%H3117>day<s%> his <S%H6250>thoughts<s%> <S%H6>perish.<s%>

Happy <S%H835><s%> is he that hath the <S%H7945>God<s%> <S%H410><s%> of <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> for his <S%H5828>help,<s%> whose <S%H7664>hope<s%> is <S%H5921>in<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> his God: <S%H430><s%>

Which <S%H6213>made<s%> <S%H8064>heaven,<s%> and <S%H776>earth,<s%> <S%H853><s%> the <S%H3220>sea,<s%> and <S%H3605>all<s%> <S%H834>that<s%> therein is: which <S%H8104>keepeth<s%> <S%H571>truth<s%> forever: <S%H5769><s%>

Which <S%H6213>executeth<s%> <S%H4941>judgment<s%> for the <S%H6231>oppressed:<s%> which <S%H5414>giveth<s%> <S%H3899>food<s%> to the <S%H7457>hungry.<s%> The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H5425>looseth<s%> the prisoners: <S%H631><s%>

The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H6491>openeth<s%> the eyes of the <S%H5787>blind:<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H2210>raiseth<s%> them that are bowed <S%H3721>down:<s%> the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H157>loveth<s%> the righteous: <S%H6662><s%>

The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> <S%H8104>preserveth<s%> <S%H853><s%> the <S%H1616>strangers;<s%> he <S%H5749>relieveth<s%> the <S%H3490>fatherless<s%> and <S%H490>widow:<s%> but the <S%H1870>way<s%> of the <S%H7563>wicked<s%> he turneth upside <S%H5791>down.<s%>

The <S%H3068>LORD<s%> shall <S%H4427>reign<s%> <S%H5769>forever,<s%> even thy <S%H430>God,<s%> O <S%H6726>Zion,<s%> unto all <S%H1755>generations.<s%> <S%H1755><s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> ye the <S%H3050>LORD.<s%>
